      <scopecontent id="aspace_59e0d00fe29e6a5c75f0b8370f2aa578">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection includes scientific articles authored by Gertrude Van Wagenen (1893-1978), a pioneer in primate research and a leading expert in reproductive endocrinology. Articles from the <title>
               <part>Yale Journal of Biology and Medicine</part>
            </title> are in complete issues.</p>
      </scopecontent>
